Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇子…镇子要出大事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人  想要让大坝决堤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是窝里斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:33.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:33.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:52.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君にもう一人きりで待たないでと　言い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:52.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:59.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色あせてく　世界の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:59.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:05.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:05.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:11.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:11.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之间  逢见君影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:15.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:15.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:27.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:27.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:30.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:30.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:33.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:33.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:45.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:45.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:55.85,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往森林走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续走就应该能看到大坝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要打开水门？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话  镇子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥镇就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在眠大人正在前往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠她？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有葛西先生最后留下了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是重次大人为了开发新药给制药公司那边的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它却出现在那个专家手上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人从一开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了吗…我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大坝的管理室工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带路就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小笠原同学…把一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃还有栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我一定要做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神堕人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  不会有事的  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  水停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗  怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我的话只杀我不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会理会怪物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原谅把三重子从我身边夺走的这个镇子和这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的怪物  准备受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生  请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就从你开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也把这些家伙说成怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  栉名田同学和小铃都不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学为了保护我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学他们为了和我们共存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才强忍着严格的戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你未婚妻的事是一场不幸的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  栉名田同学他们都不断伤害着自己而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天刚来到这里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身边发生了好多不敢相信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天为止还在的人却突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笠原同学  一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一定还有许多人不为我所知地死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我这特别的「蜜」的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学到底是带着什么样的心情保护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不觉得  这里的人们都是好人么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是怪物  怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果取走我的性命  就能够让你释怀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管理由为何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都夺走了你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无法用语言搪塞的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请您高抬贵手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过这小镇  以及这小镇上的人们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想平平安安地度过每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想过上普普通通的  与常人一样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与常人一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放屁！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没长良心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从出生到现在  我从来都没有忘记过良心二字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被大神选中的白狼观音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉大神之命  守护此嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您想要毁掉嫦娥镇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就非得先让我倒下不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:15:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}愿大家能在同一片天空下生活  署名：要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔节之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼之间  时光飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事  就如梦境一般随风而去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生活  又重回日常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不叫醒我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  你就不能再对你哥好点么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于重次他留下来的新药的开发情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重次他在九泉之下  也可以瞑目了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  猎户这个职务…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后该怎么处理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于戒律  我认为也是时候该重新审视了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  要同学  栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也还好吧  九澄？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回位子坐好  点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美  把这卷子发一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随堂抽查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏惧着「神人」的人们  都纷纷离开了这座小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新市区里  如今已然是人丁凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是在转瞬之间  就变得如同鬼城一般的冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也无法保证  那些离开了小镇的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对这段不可思议的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「神人」的存在守口如瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许终有一日  这一切会为世人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是如此  现在的静谧  也应该只会是昙花一现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔～八朔～嫦娥的八朔～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德兰泽的特级巨无霸泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠说她也想挑战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠  博士君他也要来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…  这个量很吓人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大得吓人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事  才8人份而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  我们再也没有提起过那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像这样  有事没事  闲话家常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  咱们走吧  栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以直呼其名了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫她小眠  或者眠眠之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我问题不大  只是栉名田同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  小博  快叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步  去爱德兰泽那边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神人存在的意义  以及理由」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  我也曾自己认真思考过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  那便是试着理解并接受与自己不同的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不仅仅是对于「神人」而言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是指在各种层面上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于与自己不同的存在  不是去畏惧厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是试着去包容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  小博  就练习一下试试嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  这种事就顺其自然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊  小眠你也说一句嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  请…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的我  能办到的事情  还很少很少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这份无力  我也恨自己没用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得细水长流  只要一步一步走下去  就一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神人」与我们  一定能够携起手来  共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建成一座桃源乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今  我  如是坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:18.19,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:18.19,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:28.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが信じた　愛ノ共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:28.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(425,440)\fs18}うた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:28.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信  爱之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:38.10,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱き締めた夜には　欠けた月が啼く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:38.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠  残月鸣泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.01,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には　躊躇いの月が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.01,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(363,440)\fs18}とまど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回  惑月迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:50.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}満ちる　溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:50.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}满盈圆缺  无痕冰消
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつもの心が　キミを縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:56.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结  若缚君影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:03.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}墜ちてゆく決意が許されるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:03.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则至神允  坠天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:07.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛なの、と　信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:07.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}深信此爱  永不相弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:14.69,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}微かな声　手繰りよせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:14.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:20.48,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交錯わる　闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:20.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交结暗之乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:27.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでゆく　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:27.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:37.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが夢見た　刻ノ謳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:37.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我梦  时之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑是蛙兮非蛙面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳长长兮栖水间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑是兔兮非兔颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身盈盈兮桃红见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这座仍旧是迷雾重重的嫦娥镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人难以置信的事件  正在发生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是现实  还是我的噩梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  嫦娥镇奇谈
